org.deuce.transaction
Interface Context

All Known Implementing Classes:
Context, Context, Context, Context
public interface Context

All the STM implementations should implement this interface. Using the -Dorg.deuce.transaction.contextClass property one can switch between the different implementations.

Since:
1.0
Author:
Guy Korland

rollback

void rollback()
Called on rollback, rollback might be called more than once in a row. But, can't be called after commit() without an #init(int, String)) call in between.
